{
  "key": 54359,
  "messages": [
    {
      "id": "GalacticHQ4F_Text_SpeechWasBigLie",
      "en_US": [
        "Cyrus: ...So, you’ve come.\n",
        "You heard my speech, I take it.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "GalacticHQ4F_Text_IKnowWhyYoureHere",
      "en_US": [
        "I know why you’re here. I can sense\n",
        "it in you.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "GalacticHQ4F_Text_YouAreIndeedStrong",
      "en_US": [
        "Cyrus: I see.\n",
        "You are indeed strong.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "GalacticHQ4F_Text_IMakePowerMyOwn",
      "en_US": [
        "Cyrus: The Master Ball is the ultimate\n",
        "Poké Ball.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "GalacticHQ4F_Text_TakeWarpPanel",
      "en_US": [
        "If you wish to save the Pokémon from\n",
        "the lakes, take the warp panel ahead.\r",
        "I am off to Mt. Coronet.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "GalacticHQ4F_Text_DoorIsLocked",
      "en_US": [
        "The door is locked.\n",
        "A special key is needed."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "GalacticHQ4F_Text_UseGalacticKey",
      "en_US": [
        "The door is locked.\n",
        "A special key is needed.\r",
        "Use the Galactic Key?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "GalacticHQ4F_Text_DoorOpened",
      "en_US": "The door opened."
    },
    {
      "id": "GalacticHQ4F_Text_TeamGalacticWarpPanels",
      "en_US": [
        "Team Galactic Warp Panels!\r",
        "The green warp panel returns you\n",
        "to the ground floor.\r",
        "Onward to a new universe!\n",
        "-Team Galactic"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "GalacticHQ4F_Text_TeamGalacticReport",
      "en_US": "Team Galactic Report\r"
    },
    {
      "id": "GalacticHQ4F_Text_ReadWhichReport",
      "en_US": "Which report would you like to read?"
    },
    {
      "id": "GalacticHQ4F_Text_ReportCreationOfSpace",
      "en_US": [
        "Some say the universe originated\n",
        "from a massive explosion.\r",
        "Similarly, Sinnoh is thought to have\n",
        "been formed by an explosion in\f",
        "ancient times.\r",
        "Needless to say, the explosion came\n",
        "from the power of a Pokémon.\r",
        "The Pokémon must have been the\n",
        "mythical creature considered\f",
        "a deity by the ancients.\r",
        "Our aim is not to capture the mythical\n",
        "Pokémon, but to obtain its power...\r",
        "The PC entry ends there...\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "GalacticHQ4F_Text_ReportMythicalPokemon",
      "en_US": [
        "The mythical Pokémon...\r",
        "According to myths, the Pokémon\n",
        "created Sinnoh with its power.\r",
        "However, capturing the Pokémon with\n",
        "a Poké Ball prevents it from using\f",
        "its full power...\r",
        "But with the Red Chain, the Pokémon\n",
        "can be shackled, and its power can\f",
        "be used without restraint...\r",
        "The PC entry ends there...\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "GalacticHQ4F_Text_ReportRedChain",
      "en_US": [
        "The Red Chain...\r",
        "The Pokémon of the three lakes and\n",
        "Mt. Coronet are somehow connected.\r",
        "Capturing the Pokémon of the lakes\n",
        "will free the Pokémon of Mt. Coronet.\r",
        "From the Pokémon of the lakes,\n",
        "crystals can be extracted to create\f",
        "a Red Chain.\r",
        "Using that Red Chain, the mythical\n",
        "Pokémon can be summoned and shackled\f",
        "to do as we command...\r",
        "The PC entry ends there...\r"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
